title: How Many Of These Things Have Fallen Into Your Bra
text:

Getty Images ID: 10240056 Select every item that has fallen into your bra. a few crumbs a disturbingly large number of crumbs a kernel of popcorn a handful or more of popcorn chocolate chocolate that melted a single Skittle or M&M multiple Skittles or M&Ms chip Cheeto partial cracker whole cracker rice gummy bear grape raisin olive cheese sprinkles paper clip sand cocktail weenie herbs and/or spices bobby pin lettuce granola trail mix blueberry nut pasta (dry or cooked) piece of meat coin multiple coins earring hair confetti glitter button small plastic figurine marble USB memory stick leaf twig grass bug spider several bugs or spiders quail egg baby animal Show me my results! How Many Of These Things Have Fallen Into Your Bra? You got: Perfect Human Being Wow! Your ability to not drop common items into your bra is incredible.
You got: Average Bra Dropper Gravity exists. Of course you’re going to drop some stuff down into that bra sometimes. It’s in the perfect position to catch things. But you’re pretty good at not dropping EVERYTHING down there.
You got: Bra Champion Your bra is THE PLACE to find anything you might be looking for. Your bra is a hot destination. It’s like a junk drawer, but much cooler.
